  "steps": [
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――ひだまりストア・翌日朝――",
      "bg": "images/assets/bg/battle_store_lv1.png",
      "bgMode": "forceReplace",
      "forceBackgroundReplace": true,
      "clearStorySprites": true
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――開店前のひだまりストアは、まだ少し静かだった。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "シャッターは上がっているが、店内には朝の準備の音だけが響いている。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "レジの確認。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "棚の整頓。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "バックヤードから聞こえる段ボールを動かす音。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "いつも通りの朝のはずだった。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――ただ、空気はいつもより少しだけ慎重だった。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "店長、おはようございます。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "おはよう、美空。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "昨日は……ありがとうございました。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "いや。\n俺の方こそ、心配かけた。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "本当に大丈夫ですか？\n階段から落ちたって聞いた時、心臓が止まるかと思いました。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "少し打っただけだ。\n動けるし、仕事にも支障はない。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "でも、無理はしないでくださいね。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "わかった。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "夜空も、昨日帰ってからずっと心配してました。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空は？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "来てます。\nでも、バックヤードから出てきません。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "……そっか。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "店長に会うの、怖いんだと思います。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "俺に？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "はい。\n怒ってるかもしれないって。\n嫌われたかもしれないって。\nそれに、店長の怪我が本当はひどかったらどうしようって。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "大したことないんだけどな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "それを何回言っても、たぶん夜空は確認します。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空らしいな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "はい。\nでも、今日はからかわないであげてくださいね。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "もちろん。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "わたしも、全部は聞いてません。\n夜空が言えるところだけでいいと思ったので。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "美空。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "はい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "ありがとう。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "わたしは何も。\n夜空が帰ってきてくれただけで、よかったです。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――美空はそう言って、少しだけ笑った。\nけれど、その目元にはまだ心配が残っている。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "店長、夜空のこと、お願いします。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "任せてくれ。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――ひだまりストア・バックヤード――",
      "bg": "images/assets/bg/bg_hidamari_warehouse.png",
      "bgMode": "forceReplace",
      "forceBackgroundReplace": true,
      "clearStorySprites": true
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――バックヤードには、開店前の商品箱がいくつも積まれていた。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "その奥で、夜空が一人、伝票の束を揃えている。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "手元の動きは丁寧だったが、店長が入ってきた瞬間、その指先が止まった。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "おはよう。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……おはよう。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――夜空は顔を上げない。\n伝票を見ているふりをしているが、明らかに読んではいなかった。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "昨日はちゃんと眠れたか？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……少し。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "そっか。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "言わなくていい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "うん。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……でも、聞こえててもいい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "うん。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――夜空は伝票を置く。\nそれから、ゆっくり店長の足元へ視線を落とした。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "足。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "大丈夫だ。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "肩。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "少し打ったけど、大したことない。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "腕。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "動く。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "頭。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "打ってない。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "本当に？",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "本当に。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "病院。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "必要なら行く。\n今は問題ない。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "店長はすぐ我慢する。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空もな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "昨日も言われた。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "今日も言う。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "言わなくていい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "うん。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――夜空は少しだけ唇を噛む。\nそれから、ようやく小さく頭を下げた。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……昨日は、ごめんなさい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "うん。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "押したこと。\n落としたこと。\n怪我させたかもしれないこと。\nひどいことを言ったこと。\n追いかけさせたこと。\n……泣いたこと。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "泣いたことは謝らなくていい。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "謝る。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "どうして？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "あんなの、見せるつもりじゃなかった。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "俺は、見せてもらってよかったと思ってる。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "そういうこと言わないで。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "悪い。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "謝らないで。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "うん。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……本当に、嫌いになってない？",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "なってない。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "怒ってない？",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "怒ってない。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "でも、痛かったでしょ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "押されたのは痛かった。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "でも、それで夜空を嫌いになるわけじゃない。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……ずるい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "うん。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "何を言っても、そうやって返す。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "できるだけ、そうしたい。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "できるだけって言うの、ずるい。\n絶対じゃないから、少し信じられる。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "そっか。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "言わなくていい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "うん。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "――夜空は伝票をもう一度手に取る。\nけれど、すぐにそれを置いた。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "美空に、まだ全部は言えない。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "うん。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "昨日、逃げたことは謝った。\n心配させたことも謝った。\nでも、美空のことを……。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "うん。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "ずるいって思ったことは、まだ言えない。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "今日じゃなくていい。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "言わなきゃだめ？",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "いつか、夜空が言える時でいい。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "言えないかもしれない。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "それでも、今はここに戻ってきた。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……そればっかり。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "大事なことだからな。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10101.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "夜空は昨日、帰ってきた。\n今日も、店に来た。\nそれで十分じゃないか？"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "十分じゃない。",
